To replicate the BioBench2 package setup exactly,
download the "nt" BLAST database to this folder.

See: ftp://ftp.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/blast/db/

The NCBI perl script "update_blastdb.pl" is 
useful for this purpose.  This script can be
found here:

https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/IEB/ToolBox/CPP_DOC/lxr/source/src/app/blast/update_blastdb.pl

Change permissions to make the script executable:

chmod 755 update_blastdb.pl

Then run (inside the BLAST/input directory):

./update_blastdb.pl nt

